1. Header-only library file for a simple thread-safe logger that can print to console and/or a text file.


2. Required installations
A) Install GoogleTest with:
sudo apt-get install googletest

B) Install ThreadSanitizer with:
sudo apt-get install libtsan0

3. Use GoogleTest / logger_gtest.cpp
A) Link with -lgtest -pthread
B) Compile and build

4. Use ThreadSanitizer(Data race detection test)
A)Link with -pthread
B) Compile and build
